            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>creamy pesto chicken </strong>over the <strong>warmed broccoli brown rice</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and tear over the <strong>basil leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
